# 2.2-multi-stage-essay.ms.md

<MIND_SCRIPT>
    <TARGET>text</TARGET>

    <TASK>Write a 5-section essay.</TASK>

    <DATA>{{topic}}</DATA>

    <STAGE number="1">
        Generate outline.
    </STAGE>

    <STAGE number="2">
        Expand each section to 150 words.
    </STAGE>

    <RULES>
        - Deterministic output.
        - Formal tone.
    </RULES>

    <OUTPUT>
        Sectioned essay.
    </OUTPUT>
</MIND_SCRIPT>
